title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Benefactor Vorschlaghammer
content:
Do you aspire to weave between obstacles and leave your opponents in a cloud of rubber-scented smoke? Upgrade the new Benefactor Vorschlaghammer (Sedan) with Drift Tuning at the LS Car Meet. With its German engineering, optimized handling, and all-wheel drive, it’s a chariot tailor-made for Drift Gods.

The Drift Tuning upgrade is available for free at the LS Car Meet for GTA+ Members.
